2_blank%5C%22%3Ephantom%20braking%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20the%20propensity%20for%20Teslas%20with%20autopilot%20engaged%20to%20slam%20on%20the%20brakes%20for%20imaginary%20hazards%20while%20in%20the%20full%20flow%20of%20traffic.%20At%20least%20one%20person%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-deaths%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edied%20in%20a%20Tesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20result%20of%20phantom%20braking.%20Regulators%20opened%20an%20investigation%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-phantom-braking-incidents-nhtsa-investigation-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephantom%20braking%20in%20Teslas%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%20The%20National%20Highway%20Traffic%20Safety%20Administration%2C%20the%20bureau%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Transportation%20that%20investigates%20vehicle%20defects%2C%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20the%20model%20and%20year%2C%20Teslas%20have%20two%20different%20gearshifts.%20It's%20not%20clear%20which%20model%20year%20Chao%20was%20driving%2C%20but%20both%20mechanisms%20have%20generated%20complaints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20late%202021%2C%20drivers%20of%20all%20Teslas%20shifted%20into%20reverse%20by%20depressing%20the%20brake%20pedal%20and%20flicking%20a%20gear%20stalk%20to%20the%20right%20of%20the%20steering%20wheel%20up%20%E2%80%94%20a%20motion%20that%20some%20complainants%20said%20was%20confusing%20because%2C%20for%20some%20models%20and%20years%2C%20the%20same%20motion%20on%20the%20gear%20stalk%20disengages%20the%20car's%20autopilot%20mode%20when%20the%20brake%20is%20not%20depressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20driver%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftes