ERules%20for%20relatives%20of%20employees%20vary%20from%20airline%20to%20airline.%20At%20United%20Airlines%2C%20children%20of%20airline%20employees%20usually%20lose%20their%20privileges%20when%20they%20turn%2026.%20But%20that%20won't%20apply%20to%20Crawford%2C%20as%20he's%20listed%20as%20his%20father's%20primary%20companion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20very%20grateful%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFlying%20on%20standby%20isn't%20as%20risky%20as%20you'd%20think%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Crawford%20started%20to%20realize%20how%20lucky%20he%20was%20when%20planning%20a%20trip%20to%20Coachella%2C%20the%20music%20festival%20held%20in%20the%20California%20desert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Google%20Flights%2C%20flights%20to%20Los%20Angeles%20or%20Palm%20Springs%20from%20New%20Jersey%2C%20where%20Crawford%20grew%20up%2C%20can%20run%20as%20much%20as%20%24450%20roundtrip%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0a%20price%20he%20and%20his%20sister%20didn't%20have%20to%20consider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20an%20aunt%20that%20lives%20in%20California%2C%20so%20we%20just%20stayed%20at%20her%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20like%2C%20'Wow%2C%20all%20we%20have%20to%20do%20is%20pay%20for%20the%20wristband%2C%20and%20we're%20going%20to%20Coachella.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrawford%20flies%20for%20free%20domestically%20because%20he%20travels%20on%20standby%2C%20meaning%20he%20doesn't%20have%20a%20seat%20assigned%20until%20close%20to%20the%20flight's%20departure%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Crawford%20has%20booked%20cheap%20last-minute%20vacations%20to%20Sydney%20and%20Paris%2C%20thanks%20to%20his%20status%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bairline%20nepo%20baby.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e9ebb86080194819fd937e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECrawford%20has%20booked%20cheap%20last-minute%20vacations%20to%20Sydney%20and%20Paris%2C%20thanks%20to%20his%20status%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bairline%20nepo%20baby.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Joshua%20Crawford%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECrawford%20said%20he%20doesn't%20always%20get%20on%20the%20flights%20he%20wants.%20There%20are%20times%20he's%20had%20to%20wait%20at%20a%20gate%20for%20a%20later%2C%20emptier%20flight%20when%20previous%20ones%20were%20fully%20booked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Crawford%20maintains%20that%20those%20situations%20rarely%20arise%20because%20he's%20learned%20to%20avoid%20certain%20routes%20and%20major%20airports%20during%20high-peak%20travel%20seasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20flying%20direct%20from%20LA%20to%20New%20York%20during%20the%20December%20holidays%2C%20Crawford%20usually%20does%20a%20layover%20in%20Denver%20to%20ensure%20he%20gets%20a%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20learn%20your%20route%2C%20essentially%2C%20you%20will%20realize%20you%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20options%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20doesn't%20hurt%20that%20Crawford's%20dad%20is%20privy%20to%20handy%20behind-the-scenes%20information%20like%20how%20many%20seats%20are%20left%20open%20on%20flights%20months%20before%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20usually%20not%20enlisting%20on%20a%20flight%20where%20I%20have%20a%20high%20chance%20of%20being%20booted%20off%20to%20the%20next%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20also%20really%20depends%20on%20your%20seniority%20with%20the%20company.%20My%20dad's%20been%20with%20United%20for%20quite%20some%20time%20now%2C%20so%20I'm%20definitely%20a%20higher%20priority%20%E2%80%94%20and%20very%20grateful%20for%20my%20father.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELast-minute%20jet-setting%20to%20destinations%20like%20Sydney%2C%20Tokyo%2C%20and%20Paris%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20Crawford%20takes%20longer-haul%20trips%20%E2%80%94%20often%20without%20much%20pre-planning.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHe%20can%20book%20anytime%2C%20though%20he%20said%20he%20isn't%20given%20an%20%26quot%3Bofficial%26quot%3B%20reservation%20until%20around%20a%20month%20before%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Crawford%20said%20he's%20booked%20last-minute%20trips%20to%20destinations%20including%20Japan%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Learning%20the%20best%20flight%20routes%20has%20helped%20Crawford%20avoid%20the%20risks%20of%20flying%20on%20standby.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e9ee2190413ab8e1da4c49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELearning%20the%20best%20flight%20routes%20has%20helped%20Crawford%20avoid%20the%20risks%20of%20flying%20on%20standby.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Joshua%20Crawford%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20to%20Australia%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%20by%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20like%20a%20little%20solo%20trip%2C%20and%20I%20probably%20planned%20that%20about%20two%20weeks%20before%20I%20went.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20Crawford%20said%2C%20he%20celebrated%20his%20birthday%20with%20a%20quick%20trip%20to%20Paris%20booked%20just%20a%20week%20before%20takeoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrawford%20does%20have%20to%20pay%20taxes%20when%20he%20books%20flights%20out%20of%20the%20country.%20However%2C%20they're%20normally%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20depends%20on%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20I%20was%20leaving%20Japan%2C%20and%20it%20was%20like%20%2470%20to%20get%20back%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPerks%20extend%20to%20business-class%20upgrades%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPaying%20almost%20nothing%20to%20fly%20isn't%20the%20only%20benefit%20Crawford%20gets%20as%20an%20airline%20nepo%20baby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20how%20long%20his%20father%20has%20worked%20for%20United%2C%20Crawford%20said%20he's%20also%20a%20high%20priority%20when%20free%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-class-upgrade-bidding-save-money-worth-it-virgin-atlantic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eupgrades%20to%20business%20class%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnown%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflying-on-united-polaris-great-game-changer-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPolaris%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20premium%20cabins%20feature%20spacious%20pods%20with%20seats%20that%20can%20be%20turned%20into%20lie-flat%20beds%20and%20amenities%20like%20eye%20serums%2C%20facial%20sprays%2C%20and%20hand%20creams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22On%20some%20occasions%2C%20Crawford%20has%20received%20free%20upgrades%20to%20United%20Airlines%20Polaris%20business%20class%20cabin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e9ec3690413ab8e1da4a4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20some%20occasions%2C%20Crawford%20has%20received%20free%20upgrades%20to%20United%20Airlines%20Polaris%20business%20class%20cabin.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Joshua%20Crawford%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Crawford%2C%20the%20upgrades%20help%20alleviate%20his%20jet%20lag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20flew%20to%20Sydney%20from%20LA%2C%20and%20that%20was%20about%20a%2016-hour%20flight.%20There%20and%20back%2C%20I%20was%20in%20Polaris%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20such%20a%20big%20difference%20when%20you're%20in%20that%20economy%20middle%20seat%20versus%20when%20you've%20got%20upgraded%20on%20your%20flight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20recent%20college%20grad%2C%20he%20said%20he%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20fly%20business%20class%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRound-trip%20prices%20for%20business-class%20tickets%20for%20a%20long-haul%20flight%20can%20range%20upwards%20of%20%2415%2C000%2C%26quot%3B%20Crawford%20said.%20%26quot%3BComing%20out%20of%20college%20%E2%80%94%20as%20someone%20who%20has%20student%20debt%20and%20is%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20job%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20crazy%20to%20me.%20%2415%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20I%20could%20do%20so%20much%20with%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20TikTok%2C%20Crawford%20also%20said%20he%20breezes%20past%20security%20and%20immigration%20when%20he%20leaves%20and%20reenters%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20BI%2C%20he%20said%20these%20benefits%20%E2%80%94%20Global%20Entry%20and%20TSA%20PreCheck%20%E2%80%94%20weren't%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20free%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20he%20got%20a%20discount%20on%20the%20application%20fee%20(normally%20%24100)%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebecause%20of%20his%20dad's%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairline-nepo-baby-child-of-united-employee-perks-flies-standby-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710344547000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f1c0056080194819ff522b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairline-nepo-baby-child-of-united-employee-perks-flies-standby-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20travel%20benefits%20of%20being%20related%20to%20an%20airline%20employee%20don't%20stop%20at%20free%20flights.%20Airline%20nepo%20babies%20also%20get%20free%20upgrades%20to%20business%20class.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mnoyen%40insider.com%20(Maria%20Noyen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairline-nepo-baby-child-of-united-employee-perks-flies-standby-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Interim%20Stay%20on%20Union%20Government%20Notifying%20Its%20Fact-Checking%20Unit%2C%20Says%20Bombay%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F02120845%2F2155086006_de9f5d98ef_b.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20There%20will%20be%20no%20interim%20stay%20on%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20notifying%20a%20fact-checking%20unit%20(FCU)%20as%20per%20its%20amended%20Information%20Technology%20(IT)%20rules%2C%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20(March%2013).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20more%20than%20a%20month%20after%20a%20two-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20high%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbombay-hc-split-verdict-petition-it-amendment-rules%5C%22%3Edelivered%20a%20split%20verdict%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20specific%20rule%20dealing%20with%20the%20FCU%20and%20two%20days%20after%20a%20tie-breaker%20judge%20said%20there%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fmaharashtra%2Fbombay-hc-refuses-to-grant-interim-stay-on-setting-up-fact-checking-unit-to-identify-fake-news-against-govt-2931452%5C%22%3Eno%20case%20for%20stopping%20the%20government%20from%20notifying%20an%20FCU%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20third%20judge%20has%20rendered%20his%20opinion.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20majority%20view%20is%20that%20the%20interim%20applications%20for%20stay%20and%20continuation%20of%20the%20previous%20statement%20(by%20the%20Union%20%5Bgovernment%5D%20not%20to%20notify%20the%20FCU)%20are%20rejected%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Ffact-check-unit-bombay-high-court-central-govt-it-rules-amendment-2023-social-media-content-252162%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20the%20reconstituted%20two-judge%20bench%20as%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20split%20verdict%20on%20January%2031%2C%20the%20petitioners%20in%20the%20case%2C%20among%20whom%20is%20comedian%20Kunal%20Kamra%2C%20sought%20an%20interim%20stay%20on%20the%20FCU%20being%20notified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meity.gov.in%2Fwritereaddata%2Ffiles%2FInformation%2520Technology%2520%2528Intermediary%2520Guidelines%2520and%2520Digital%2520Media%2520Ethics%2520Code%2529%2520Rules%252C%25202021%2520%2528updated%252006.04.2023%2529-.pdf%5C%22%3ERule%203(1)(b)(v)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20amended%20rule%20that%20the%20petitioners%20have%20challenged%2C%20says%20that%20an%20FCU%20can%20identify%20content%20online%20relating%20to%20%E2%80%9Cany%20business%20of%20the%20central%20%5BUnion%5D%20government%E2%80%9D%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfake%2C%20false%20or%20misleading%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20FCU%20makes%20such%20an%20identification%2C%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%20would%20either%20have%20to%20take%20down%20the%20content%20in%20question%20or%20add%20a%20disclaimer%20mentioning%20the%20FCU%E2%80%99s%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20split%20verdict%20made%20in%20January%2C%20Justice%20Gautam%20Patel%20said%20that%20rule%203(1)(b)(v)%20must%20be%20struck%20down%20but%20Justice%20Neela%20Gokhale%20upheld%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20referred%20the%20matter%20to%20a%20third%20judge%2C%20Justice%20A.S.%20Chandurkar%2C%20for%20a%20decision%20in%20order%20to%20resolve%20the%20impasse.%20He%20was%20also%20meant%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20petitions%20seeking%20an%20interim%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Chandurkar%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20decided%20on%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20rule%20in%20question%20but%20on%20Monday%20(March%2011)%2C%20he%20said%20regarding%20the%20interim%20petition%20that%20there%20was%20no%20case%20for%20the%20government%20to%20be%20stopped%20from%20notifying%20an%20FCU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20no%20case%20is%20made%20out%20to%20direct%20the%20respondent%20(Centre)%20%5Bthe%20Union%20government%5D%20to%20continue%20its%20statement%20that%20the%20fact-checking%20unit%20would%20not%20be%20notified%20pending%20proceedings%20on%20the%20petitions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20according%20to%20the%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20said%20the%20FCU%20will%20not%20seek%20to%20censor%20political%20opinions%2C%20satire%20or%20comedy%20and%20that%20the%20FCU%E2%80%99s%20actions%20will%20still%20be%20subject%20to%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20final%20decision%20on%20the%20rule%20in%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbalance%20of%20convenience%20tilts%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20non-applicants%20%5Bthe%20Union%20government%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freepressjournal.in%2Fmumbai%2Fbombay-hc-refuses-interim-stay-on-fact-checking-unit-notification-under-amended-it-rules%5C%22%3Ehe%20said%20according%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EFree%20Press%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20say%20the%20amended%20IT%20rules%20will%20allow%20the%20government%20to%20unilaterally%20and%20arbitrarily%20take%20decisions%20what%20is%20or%20isn%E2%80%99t%20true%20and%20pose%20a%20danger%20to%20the%20freedom%20of%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20had%20earlier%20said%20it%20would%20not%20notify%20the%20fact-checking%20unit%20until%20the%20high%20court%20took%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20rule%20in%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20solicitor%20general%20Tushar%20Mehta%20said%20after%20the%20split%20verdict%20that%20this%20assurance%20would%20continue%20only%20until%20the%20court%20took%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20interim%20stay%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710344536000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F02120845%2F2155086006_de9f5d98ef_b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fno-interim-stay-notification-fact-checking-unit-bombay-hc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Earlier%20this%20week%2C%2