2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20topical%20treatment%20prevents%20three%20common%20intestinal%20parasites%3A%20roundworms%2C%20hookworms%2C%20and%20whipworms.%20It%20also%20prevents%20flea%20infestations%20by%20killing%20adult%20fleas%20before%20they%20can%20lay%20eggs%20and%20prevents%20heartworm%20and%20mange%20mites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChoosing%20between%20an%20oral%20or%20topical%20parasite%20product%20can%20be%20a%20tough%20decision.%20Sometimes%2C%20dogs%20do%20better%20with%20one%20versus%20the%20other.%20%26quot%3BSome%20animals%20can't%20tolerate%20or%20have%20a%20food%20allergy%20to%20an%20oral%20product%2C%20so%20they%20must%20use%20a%20topical%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Melissa%20Smits%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortmorganvetclinic.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFort%20Morgan%20Veterinary%20Clinic%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BOr%20their%20skin%20may%20be%20sensitive%20to%20a%20topical%20so%20an%20oral%20is%20better.%26quot%3B%20If%20your%20dog%20has%20no%20tolerance%20issues%2C%20it%20usually%20comes%20down%20to%20your%20preference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvantage%20Multi%20is%20easy%20to%20use%3A%20You%20apply%20it%20every%2030%20days%20to%20the%20skin%20at%20the%20base%20of%20your%20dog's%20neck%20between%20the%20shoulder%20blades.%20The%20liquid%20is%20absorbed%20and%20dries%20within%20hours.%20Unlike%20with%20some%20other%20topical%20preventives%2C%20you%20do%20not%20need%20to%20wear%20gloves%20to%20apply%20it.%20If%20you%20get%20the%20product%20on%20your%20hands%2C%20simply%20wash%20them%20with%20soap%20and%20water.%20For%20the%20first%2030%20minutes%20after%20application%2C%20keep%20dogs%20from%20licking%20the%20application%20site%2C%20either%20on%20themselves%20or%20other%20treated%20dogs%20in%20the%20house.%20Children%20should%20not%20touch%20the%20application%20site%20for%20two%20hours%20after%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0As%20with%20all%20medications%20that%20prevent%20heartworm%2C%20your%20dog%20needs%20a%20heartworm%20test%20before%20starting%20Advantage%20Multi%20and%20annually%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20selected%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20selected%20the%20best%20dog%20dewormers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20researching%20and%20writing%20this%20guide%2C%20I%20drew%20from%20my%20eight%20years%20of%20experience%20as%20an%20assistant%20in%20veterinary%20hospitals%20and%20two%20decades%20of%20experience%20as%20a%20writer%20and%20editor%20in%20the%20pet%20and%20veterinary%20fields.%20I%20conducted%20research%20using%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcapcvet.org%2Fparasite-product-applications%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQuick%20Product%20Reference%20Guide%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20by%20the%20independent%2C%20nonprofit%20Companion%20Animal%20Parasite%20Council.%20This%20helpful%20reference%2C%20which%20includes%20all%20FDA-%20and%20EPA-approved%20parasite%20control%20products%20for%20small%20animals%2C%20lists%20each%20product's%20active%20ingredients%2C%20how%20the%20product%20is%20used%2C%20and%20which%20parasites%20it%20controls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20consulted%20with%20two%20licensed%20veterinarians%20for%20advice%20regarding%20the%20treatment%20and%20prevention%20of%20intestinal%20parasites%20like%20tapeworms%2C%20roundworms%2C%20and%20hookworms%2C%20as%20well%20as%20heartworms%20and%20ectoparasites%20like%20fleas%2C%20ticks%2C%20and%20mites.%20Although%20this%20information%20guided%20our%20product%20selection%2C%20our%20experts%20did%20not%20specifically%20endorse%20or%20recommend%20any%20of%20the%20products%20in%20this%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20main%20attributes%20I%20looked%20for%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafety%20and%20efficacy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Only%20FDA-approved%20products%20were%20considered%20for%20this%20guide.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumber%20of%20parasites%20treated%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20general%2C%20products%20that%20covered%20more%20parasites%20received%20higher%20ratings.%20This%20did%20not%20apply%20to%20tapeworm%20dewormers%2C%20which%20are%20only%20intended%20to%20treat%20one%20parasite.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Products%20received%20lower%20ratings%20if%20they%20were%20more%20complicated%20to%20use%20than%20a%20similar%20product.%20For%20example%2C%20lower%20ratings%20were%20given%20if%20gloves%20need%20to%20be%20worn%20to%20apply%20the%20product%20or%20if%20children%20and%20pets%20need%20to%20be%20kept%20away%20from%20the%20treated%20animal%20for%20a%20period%20of%20time%20after%20application.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMinimum%20age%20and%20weight%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20comparing%20similar%20products%2C%20higher%20scores%20went%20to%20preventives%20that%20can%20be%20used%20in%20younger%20animals.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EDog%20dewormer%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20most%20effective%20dewormer%20for%20dogs%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20different%20parasite%20preventives%20cover%20many%20different%20parasites%2C%20no%20one%20product%20covers%20every%20single%20internal%20and%20external%20parasite%20that%20could%20affect%20your%20dog.%20Talk%20to%20your%20veterinarian%20to%20help%20you%20decide%20which%20product%20will%20be%20best%20for%20your%20dog.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20most%20important%20part%20of%20having%20a%20relationship%20with%20a%20veterinarian%20in%20your%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Smits.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20trained%20to%20know%20what%20parasite%20problems%20we%20have%20in%20our%20area%20are%2C%20what%20lifestyle%20risks%20are%20important%20to%20consider%2C%20and%20overall%2C%20what%20is%20best%20for%20an%20individual%20pet%20and%20lifestyle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20I%20deworm%20my%20dog%20myself%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20some%20dewormers%20are%20available%20without%20a%20prescription%2C%20do%20not%20skip%20the%20vet%20visit%20since%20different%20drugs%20treat%20different%20worms.%20Your%20vet%20will%20perform%20a%20physical%20exam%20and%20a%20fecal%20test%20to%20determine%20what%20type%20of%20worms%20they%20have.%20%26quot%3BNot%20all%20intestinal%20parasites%20are%20created%20equal%2C%20and%20there%20is%20not%20a%20one-size-fits-all%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20deworming%20medications%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2260%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fkelley-lay-dvm-5765b8205%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Kelley%20Lay%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20relief%20veterinarian%20in%20Nashville%2C%20Tennessee.%20Although%20a%20broad-spectrum%20dewormer%20kills%20several%20different%20types%20of%20worms%2C%20certain%20single-celled%20microscopic%20parasites%20(protozoa)%2C%20including%20coccidia%20and%20Giardia%2C%20are%20not%20true%20worms.%20They%20require%20different%20prescription%20medications%20to%20treat%20them.%20Your%20dog%20also%20might%20need%20follow-up%20deworming%20and%20another%20fecal%20exam%20to%20ensure%20no%20parasites%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20natural%20dewormers%20work%20for%20dogs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENatural%20dewormers%20aren't%20necessarily%20a%20better%20option%2C%20so%20you%20should%20check%20with%20your%20veterinarian%20before%20giving%20one%20to%20your%20dog.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20'natural'%20deworming%20products%20may%20have%20some%20effect%20on%20intestinal%20parasites%2C%20I've%20consulted%20with%20numerous%20clients%20over%20the%20years%20who%20have%20tried%20them%20with%20repeated%20failure%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Lay.%20She%20adds%20that%20conventional%2C%20veterinarian-recommended%20dewormers%20have%20gone%20through%20stringent%20drug%20trials%20and%20studies%20to%20prove%20they%20are%20effective%20and%20safe%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20can%20I%20give%20my%20dog%20to