20the%20alliance%20had%20a%20smooth%20run%20in%20the%20last%20four%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20restlessness%20was%20growing%20among%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20possibly%20because%20Dushyant%20was%20hogging%20more%20limelight%2C%20something%20he%20also%20mentioned%20in%20his%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20curtains%20finally%20closed%20on%20the%20alliance%2C%20Dushyant%2C%20as%20expected%2C%20owned%20several%20achievements%20of%20Khattar%20government%20as%20his%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20whether%2050%25%20reservation%20of%20women%20in%20local%20bodies%2C%20or%2075%25%20reservations%20for%20Haryana%20youth%20in%20private%20jobs%2C%20all%20these%20welfare%20schemes%20became%20possible%20in%20the%20Khattar%20government%20because%20of%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20active%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDushyant%20said%20it%20was%20because%20of%20the%20JJP%20that%20interest%20of%20farmers%2C%20labourers%20and%20Dalits%20got%20prominence%20and%20were%20given%20benefit%20of%20government%20schemes.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CI%20am%20hopeful%20that%20the%20new%20government%20under%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20will%20continue%20welfare%20schemes%20started%20in%20the%20previous%20government%20because%20of%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDusyant%E2%80%99s%20father%20and%20JJP%E2%80%99s%20national%20president%20Ajay%20Chautala%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20also%20hinted%20that%20seat%20sharing%20dispute%20was%20cited%20as%20an%20excuse%20to%20end%20the%20alliance.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWe%20demanded%20two%20seats%20from%20the%20BJP%20but%20they%20denied%20and%20later%20snapped%20the%20ties%20with%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20while%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20saffron%20party%20saying%20that%20the%20latter%20did%20not%20follow%20alliance%20dharma.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWe%20supported%20BJP%20on%20all%20occasions%20but%20they%20did%20not.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20next%20course%20of%20action%2C%20both%20the%20father-son%20duo%20said%20they%20would%20definitely%20fight%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20they%20would%20decide%20in%20coming%20days%20on%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20that%20they%20would%20contest.%C2%A0They%20said%20their%20final%20goal%20is%20to%20get%20majority%20on%20their%20own%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%20later%20this%20year%20and%20for%20this%2C%20the%20party%20workers%20were%20fully%20poised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fharyana-cm-manohar-lal-khattar-resigns-amid-rift-between-bjp-jjp-alliance-over-seat-sharing%5C%22%3EHaryana%3A%20BJP%20Picks%20State%20Chief%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20as%20New%20CM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJJP%20came%20into%20existence%20only%20in%202018%2C%20after%20Ajay%20had%20a%20fall%20out%20with%20his%20brother%20Abhay%20Chautala%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD)%2C%20whose%20founder%20was%20popular%20Jat%20leader%20of%20Haryana%20Chaudhary%20Devi%20Lal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaini%20won%20floor%20test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20taking%20the%20oath%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20Saini%20won%20the%20floor%20test%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20due%20to%20support%20of%20six%20independent%20MLAs.%20The%20Haryana%20assembly%20was%20convened%20on%20the%20request%20of%20Saini%20who%20wanted%20to%20prove%20his%20majority%20in%20the%20floor%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20trust%20vote%2C%20five%20out%20of%20the%2010%20JJP%20MLAs%20were%20present%20in%20the%20assembly.%20But%20after%20the%20JJP%20issued%20whip%20asking%20their%20MLAs%20to%20not%20attend%20the%20session%2C%20they%20went%20out%20and%20did%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20floor%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJJP%20state%20president%20Nishan%20Singh%20told%20media%20that%20all%20party%20MLAs%20are%20united%20even%20as%20divide%20in%20the%20party%20was%20clearly%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20rally%2C%20Dushyant%20said%20that%20JJP%20was%20least%20worried%20of%20defection%20in%20the%20party.%20He%20mentioned%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%2070s%2C%20the%20then%20Congress%20leader%20Bhajan%20Lal%20took%20away%20most%20of%20our%20MLAs%20but%20did%20it%20finish%20us%3F%20Our%20real%20strength%20is%20our%20supporters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Saini%20said%20in%20his%20assembly%20address%20that%20people%20of%20the%20state%20have%20full%20confidence%20in%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20innumerable%20works%20that%20have%20been%20done%20by%20our%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Saini%20in%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20Congress%20MLAs%20flayed%20the%20BJP%2C%20saying%20that%20change%20in%20the%20government%20showed%20that%20the%20party%20was%20a%20failure%20on%20all%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710341425000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13200940%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-13-at-8.09.12-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjjps-dushyant-hits-out-at-bjp-says-entire-political-drama-was-to-unseat-him%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meanwhile%2C%20new%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%20Nayab%20Saini%20won%20the%20floor%20test%20in%20the%20assembly%20with%20the%20support%20of%20independent%20MLAs%3B%20JJP%20MLAs%20stayed%20away%20after%20party%20issued%20whip.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjjps-dushyant-hits-out-at-bjp-says-entire-political-drama-was-to-unseat-him%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rs%207%20Lakh%20'Fee'%2C%20Haryana%20Resort%3A%20UP%20Police%20Crack%20Exam%20Paper%20Leak%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20associate%20of%20a%20Delhi%20Police%20constable%20was%20arrested%20by%20a%20special%20task%20force%20of%20his%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20colleagues%20Wednesday%20evening%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20exam%20paper%20leak%20case.%20The%20UP%20team%20is%20trying%20to%20arrest%20the%20Delhi%20cop%2C%20also%20an%20accused.%20His%20associate%20is%20Mahendra%20Sharma%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Haryana's%20Jind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20around%201%2C000%20aspirants%20were%20contacted%20by%20the%20Delhi%20policeman%20and%20assembled%20-%20some%20were%20moved%20in%20buses%20-%20at%20a%20resort%20in%20Haryana%2C%20where%20they%20were%20given%20the%20answer%20key%20and%20the%20question%20paper%20for%20the%20UP%20Police%20Constable%20exam%20held%20on%20February%2017%20and%2018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhones%20and%20gadgets%20were%20seized%2C%20and%20they%20were%20made%20to%20commit%20answers%20to%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20has%20seen%20visuals%20from%20the%20'cram%20session'%20-%20held%20two%20days%20before%20the%20exam%20-%20which%20shows%20dozens%20of%20young%20men%20and%20women%20sitting%20in%20rows%20on%20a%20lawn%20and%20reading%20from%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20each%20person%20paid%20Rs%207%20lakh%20-%20to%20be%20paid%20after%20the%20exam%20-%20for%20leaked%20papers.%20The%20accused%20would%20retain%20original%20marksheets%20from%20previous%20exams%20as%20%26quot%3Binsurance%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exam%20papers%20and%20answer%20keys%20were%20procured%20from%20two%20other%20people%2C%20identified%20simply%20as%20Abhishek%20Shukla%2C%20from%20UP's%20Prayagraj%2C%20and%20Ravi%20Attri%2C%20who%20is%20a%20resident%20of%20UP's%20Greater%20Noida%20and%20was%20involved%20in%20the%202015%20AIPMT%2C%20or%20All%20India%20Pre-Medical%20and%20Pre-Dental%20Test%2C%20paper%20leak%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20believe%20Attri%20and%20Shukla%20could%20be%20the%20final%20pieces%20in%20this%20jigsaw%20puzzle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20arrest%20and%20interrogation%20of%20Ravi%20and%20Abhishek%20could%20be%20the%20last%20link%20in%20this%20investigation%20and%20efforts%20are%20being%20made%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Additional%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Brijesh%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday's%20arrest%20comes%20a%20month%20after%2015%20others%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%20for%20allegedly%20planning%20to%20leak%20question%20papers%20for%20the%20same%20exam.%20In%20that%20instance%20the%20accused%20were%20taking%20payments%20upto%20Rs%208%20lakh%20per%20aspirant.%20That%20edition%20of%20the%20exam%20was%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-cancels-police-constable-recruitment-exam-after-paper-leak-allegations-5118905%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUP%20Cancels%20Police%20Constable%20Recruitment%20Exam%2C%20Orders%20Re-Test%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2048%20lakh%20men%20and%20women%20sat%20for%20that%20exam%2C%20which%20was%20cancelled%20days%20later%20amid%20multiple%20paper%20leak%20reports.%20UP%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20can%20be%20no%20compromise%20with%20the%20sanctity%20of%20examinations.%20Those%20who%20toy%20with%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20youngsters%20will%20not%20be%20spared%20under%20any%20circumstances.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnational-sin-yogi-adityanath-vows-strict-against-up-exam-paper-leak-5124559%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BNational%20Sin%26quot%3B%3A%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20Vows%20Strict%20In%20UP%20Exam%20Paper%20Leak%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20last%20month%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20passed%20an%20'anti-cheating'%20bill%20to%20check%20fraudulent%20practices%20such%20as%20these%20-%20the%20leaking%20of%20exam%20papers%20for%20government%20recruitment%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-passes-