ouse%2C%20however%2C%20is%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20official%20figures%20from%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20own%20election%20office.%20It%20remains%20unclear%20from%20where%20the%20chief%20minister%20sourced%20his%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbroad-consensus-in-manipur-that-state-responsible-for-ethnic-violence%5C%22%3EManipur%3A%20Both%20Centre%20and%20State%20Played%20a%20Principal%20Role%20in%20Ethnic%20Violence%2C%20Claims%20Fact-Finding%20Team%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDecadal%20figures%20as%20per%20the%20election%20office%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20statement%20in%20the%20House%2C%20the%20office%20of%20the%20election%20commissioner%20presents%20a%20different%20picture%20of%20the%20decadal%20growth%20of%20the%20population%20of%20the%20Kuki%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20legislative%20constituencies%20such%20as%20Tengnoupal%2C%20Saikul%2C%20Kangpokpi%2C%20and%20Thanlon%20registered%20a%20negative%20growth%20in%20their%20electorate%20size%2C%20whereas%20Saitu%2C%20Tipaimukh%2C%20Henglep%2C%20Churachandpur%2C%20Saikot%2C%20and%20Singhat%20registered%20some%20growth%20in%20electorate%20size%20%3Cem%3E(see%20Table%202%3C%2Fem%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChurachandpur%20and%20Saikot%20constituencies%2C%20however%2C%20registered%20a%20high%20decadal%20growth%20in%20the%20electorate%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20this%20drastic%20increase%20for%20the%20two%20constituencies%20is%20not%20far%20to%20seek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirstly%2C%20Churachandpur%20town%20%E2%80%93%20which%20includes%20Saikot%20constituency%20%E2%80%93%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20urbanised%20hill%20towns%2C%20attracting%20Kuki%20people%20migrating%20from%20different%20districts%20within%20the%20state%20in%20search%20of%20better%20life%20and%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20the%20to