22%3A%22The%20EU's%20AI%20Act%20seeks%20to%20counter%20the%20risks%20associated%20with%20the%20rapidly%20growing%20AI%20sector.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A95%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-68546450%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-68546450.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-68546450.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Didi'%20Bets%20On%20'Didi%20No.1'%20Star%20To%20Woo%20Women%20Voters%20Amid%20Sandeshkhali%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20was%20an%20award%20for%20glitz%20quotient%20in%20announcing%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20candidates%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%20would%20be%20a%20clear%20winner.%C2%A0While%20other%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20put%20out%20lacklustre%20lists%20with%20names%20of%20candidates%20and%20the%20seats%20they%20were%20chosen%20for%2C%20Trinamool%20hosted%20a%20gala%20event%20in%20Kolkata's%20Brigade%20ground%20last%20weekend%20to%20introduce%20its%20poll%20picks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20led%20the%20parade%2C%20waving%20to%20the%20crowd%20and%20followed%20by%20the%20party's%2042%20candidates%20for%20as%20many%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Bengal.%20Her%20nephew%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20virtually%20the%20No.2%20in%20the%20party%2C%20read%20out%20the%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20surprise%20choice%20walked%20right%20behind%20the%20Trinamool%20chief.%20It%20is%20a%20face%20that%20keeps%20Bengali%20women%20in%20and%20outside%20the%20state%20hooked%20to%20the%20TV%20screen%20for%20an%20hour%20daily.%20It%20was%20the%20face%20of%20Rachna%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2049-year-old%2C%20who%20was%20born%20Jhumjhum%20Banerjee%2C%20first%20made%20headlines%20back%20in%201994%2C%20when%20she%20was%20crowned%20Miss%20Kolkata.%20She%20later%20went%20on%20to%20star%20in%20films%20across%20several%20languages%2C%20including%20Bengali%2C%20Odia%2C%20Telugu%2C%20Tamil%20and%20Kannada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20no%20film%20won%20her%20the%20popularity%20that%20a%20TV%20game%20show%20did.%20'Didi%20No.%201'%20was%20launched%20in%202010%20and%20interestingly%2C%20Rachna%20Banerjee%20was%20not%20its%20first%20anchor.%20She%20took%20over%20in%20the%20second%20season%20and%20then%20the%20producers%20tried%20other%20faces%20too%2C%20but%20none%20stuck%20on%20the%20way%20she%20did.%20The%20show%20has%20a%20bit%20of%20everything%20-%20games%2C%20laughter%20and%20emotions.%20Women%20participants%20narrate%20their%20life%20struggles%2C%20share%20their%20happy%20memories%20and%20the%20anchor%20balances%20fun%20and%20sentimentality.%20The%20result%20is%20the%20longest%20running%20Bengali%20game%20show%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20weeks%20before%20the%20Trinamool%20announced%20its%20candidates%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20starred%20in%20a%20Didi%20No.%201%20episode.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20few%20people%20had%20thought%20that%20Rachna%20Banerjee%20would%20be%20the%20Trinamool's%20poll%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20celebrity%20candidate%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Hooghly%2C%20a%20suburban%20seat%20near%20Kolkata.%20She%20is%20up%20against%20a%20former%20colleague%20and%20actor-turned-politician%2C%20BJP's%20Locket%20Chatterjee.%20Ms%20Chatterjee%20is%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Hooghly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool's%20choice%20of%20Rachna%20Banerjee%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20mood%20of%20this%20election.%C2%A0The%20biggest%20political%20talking%20point%20in%20Bengal%20right%20now%20is%20Sandeshkhali.%20An%20island%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%2C%20Sandeshkhali%20has%20made%20headlines%20after%20its%20residents%20accused%20local%20Trinamool%20leaders%20of%20land%20grab%2C%20extortion%20and%20sexual%20harassment.%20While%20Trinamool%20has%20expelled%20its%20local%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20now%20in%20CBI's%20custody%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20mob%20attack%20case%2C%20the%20Oppositon%20BJP%20has%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20its%20efforts%20to%20paint%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20%26quot%3Banti-women%26quot%3B.%20Over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20chief%20has%20cultivated%20a%20formidable%20support%20base%20among%20women%20through%20schemes%20like%20Kanyashree%2C%20Rupashree%20and%20Lakshmir%20Bhandar.%20That%20is%20now%20under%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20Rachna%20Banerjee%20comes%20in.%20Yes%2C%20she%20is%20a%20celebrity%2C%20but%20her%20audience%20cuts%20across%20the%20urban-rural%20divide%20and%20spans%20age%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20has%20repeatedly%20propped%20up%20actors%20as%20its%20poll%20picks%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20is%20well%20aware%20that%20the%20glitz%20advantage%20comes%20at%20a%20cost.%20Outgoing%20MPs%20Mimi%20Chakraborty%20and%20Nusrat%20Jahan%20pulled%20off%20stunning%20wins%20in%20the%202019%20election%2C%20but%20the%20party%20had%20to%20tackle%20the%20side-effects%20too.%20Nusrat%20Jahan%2C%20for%20example%2C%20drew%20fire%20for%20posting%20a%20clip%20of%20her%20Valentine's%20Day%20celebrations%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20row.%20This%20prompted%20rivals%20to%20target%20the%20Trinamool%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20propping%20up%20candidates%20not%20invested%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20strategy%20has%20paid%20off%20for%20Ms%20Banerjee%20so%20far.%20Hence%2C%20the%20former%20celebrity%20picks%20have%20made%20way%20for%20new%20ones.%20But%20with%20Rachana%20Banerjee%2C%20Trinamool%20is%20looking%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20a%20far%20wider%20demographic%20than%20it%20has%20earlier%20done.%20Unlike%20Mimi%20Chakraborty%2C%20Nusrat%20Jahan%20or%20actor%20Dev%20-%20who%20has%20been%20repeated%20as%20a%20candidate%20this%20time%20-%20Rachna%20comes%20on%20TV%20daily.%20Her%20audience%20spans%20across%20economic%20classes%20and%20both%20urban%20and%20rural%20belts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20a%20sea%20of%20difference%20between%20a%20TV%20studio%20and%20the%20poll%20arena.%20Rachana%20Banerjee%20knows%20there%20are%20no%20retakes%20here.%20In%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20she%20has%20said%20the%20shooting%20of%20Didi%20No%201%20may%20face%20disruptions%20over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20months.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20be%20campaigning%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20But%20I%20will%20come%20and%20shoot%20at%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Then%20came%20the%20big%20question%3A%20why%20politics%3F%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe%20need%20power%20and%20a%20platform%20to%20work%20for%20people%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20bigger%20platform%20than%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710331020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F1pt3bnno_rachna-banerjee-mamata-banerjee_625x300_13_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsandeshkhali-mamata-banerjee-rachna-banerjee-didi-bets-on-didi-no-1-star-to-woo-women-voters-amid-sandeshkhali-row-5231370%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20there%20was%20an%20award%20for%20glitz%20quotient%20in%20announcing%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20candidates%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%20would%20be%20a%20clear%20winner.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsandeshkhali-mamata-banerjee-rachna-banerjee-didi-bets-on-didi-no-1-star-to-woo-women-voters-amid-sandeshkhali-row-5231370%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Details%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20will%20be%20disclosed%20on%20time%3A%20CEC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710330614000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108466772%2Cimgsize-19206.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fdetails-on-