%20are%20playing%20against%20each%20other.%20Not%20a%20lot%20of%20England%20players%20are%20picked%20in%20the%20IPL%2C%20mainly%20because%20they%20can%20be%20withdrawn%20by%20their%20Board%20anytime%20for%20a%20preparation%20camp%20or%20something%2C%20which%20leaves%20the%20franchises%20in%20a%20lurch%2C%26quot%3B%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20wrote%20in%20a%20column%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsportstar.thehindu.com%2Fcricket%2Franji-trophy-match-fees-doubled-india-test-cricket-fees-bcci-ind-eng%2Farticle67942378.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESportstar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20them%20can't%20stomach%20the%20fees%20for%20which%20some%20of%20the%20Indian%20players%20are%20bought%20and%20compare%20their%20achievements%20at%20the%20international%20level%20when%20the%20IPL%20auction%20dynamics%20can%20be%20so%20volatile%20and%20hard%20to%20explain%20or%20even%20understand.%20So%20you%20see%20more%20lip%20in%20the%20India-England%20encounters%20than%20in%20any%20other%20India%20match.%20That's%20why%20the%20pleasure%20of%20beating%20England%20is%20always%20greater.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%20also%20gave%20his%20take%20on%20England's%20Bazball.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Ben%20Stokes'%20team%20came%20to%20India%2C%20there%20was%20a%20buzz%20around%20it%20as%20they%20had%20started%20to%20play%20a%20brand%20of%20aggressive%20batting%20that%20the%20British%20media%20dubbed%20'Bazball'.%20This%20was%20because%20the%20new%20coach%20Brendon%20McCullum's%20nickname%20is%20'Baz'.%20He%20encouraged%20the%20players%20to%20always%20go%20in%20with%20a%20positive%20mindset%20and%20to%20keep%20at%20it%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20result.%20The%20batting%20thus%20became%20ultra-aggressive%2C%20with%20players%20encouraged%20to%20hit%20sixes%20and%20fours%20with%20a%20dot%20ball%20as%20the%20least%20preferred%20option.%20Stokes%20wanted%20his%20players%20to%20play%20like%20rock%20stars%2C%20whatever%20that%20me