C%20potters%2C%20urban%20roadside%20vendors%2C%20tailors%2C%20barbers%20as%20well%20as%20unpaid%20workers%20in%20small%20household%20enterprises%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20share%20of%20women%20in%20casual%20employment%20dropped%20sharply%20from%2028.7%25%20to%2017.1%25%20between%202011-12%20and%202022-23%2C%20the%20forum%20Bahutva%20Karnataka%20underlined%20in%20its%20report%20on%20employment%2C%20wages%20and%20inequity.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20share%20of%20men%20in%20casual%20employment%20dropped%20from%2028.2%25%20to%2022.8%25%20in%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20report%20pointed%20out%20that%209.79%20lakh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2F979-lakh-vacancies-in-central-govt-departments-jitendra-singh-11670505730311.html%5C%22%3Evacant%20posts%3C%2Fa%3E%20exist%20in%20central%20government%20jobs%20alone%2C%20as%20per%20a%20response%20given%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20Minister%20of%20State%20Jitendra%20Singh%20in%20December%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fstagnant-job-rate-worse-for-the-educated-iim-study%5C%22%3EStagnant%20Job%20Rate%2C%20Worse%20for%20the%20Educated%3A%20IIM%20Study%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20share%20of%20men%20in%20regular%20wage%20work%20has%20increased%20by%20merely%203%20percentage%20points%20from%2020.3%25%20in%202011-12%20to%2023.8%25%20in%202022-23%20and%20about%203.8%20percentage%20points%20for%20women%20%E2%80%94%2014.8%25%20in%202011-12%20to%2018.6%25%20in%202022-23%20%E2%80%94%20the%20report%20mentioned%20based%20on%20National%20Sample%20Survey%20(NSS)%20and%20the%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey%20(PLFS)%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReality%20check%3A%20too%20many%20claims%20without%20results%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202023%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.narendramodi.in%2Ftext-of-prime-minister-narendra-modis-address-at-the-distribution-of-51000-plus-appointment-letters-under-rozgar-mela-575508%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20government%20is%20working%20in%20mission%20mode%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20future%20of%20the%20youth.%E2%80%9D%20In%20a%20sharp%20contrast%2C%20the%20report%20noted%20that%2042%25%20of%20the%20graduates%20under%20the%20age%20of%2025%20are%20unemployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20underlined%20that%20the%20BJP%20manifesto%20in%202019%20mentioned%3A%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20our%20government%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%2042%25%20growth%20in%20the%20national%20minimum%20wage.%20We%20will%20maintain%20the%20same%20direction%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years%20to%20ensure%20a%20respectable%20living%20for%20the%20workers.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20nearly%2030%20crore%20people%20are%20earning%20less%20than%20the%20national%20minimum%20floor%20wages%20or%20their%20earnings%20can%20be%20considered%20too%20harsh%20to%20live%20in%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20like%20the%20combined%20population%20of%20Germany%2C%20France%2C%20UK%2C%20Spain%2C%20Netherlands%2C%20Portugal%20and%20Ireland%20living%20in%20dire%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bahutva%20Karnataka%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20an%20expert%20committee%20on%20wages%20led%20by%20Anoop%20Satpathy%20in%202019%20had%20said%20that%20the%20national%20minimum%20floor%20wages%20in%20India%20should%20be%20at%20least%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1564590%5C%22%3ERs%20375%20per%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20calculated%20based%20on%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20needed%20to%20ensure%20a%20balanced%20diet%20for%20each%20person%20%E2%80%94%20the%20committee%20also%20recommended%20an%20additional%20housing%20allowance%20of%20Rs%201%2C430%20per%20month%20for%20urban%20workers.%20However%2C%20none%20of%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20committee%20which%20was%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Labour%20and%20Employment%C2%A0were%20adopted%20by%20the%20government%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202024%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20us%20development%20means%20the%20development%20of%20the%20poorest%20of%20the%20poor%2C%20development%20of%20Dalit%2C%20tribals%2C%20backwards%20and%20deprived.%20%E2%80%9D%20The%20report%20underlined%20that%20nominal%20per%20capita%20GDP%20(total%20GDP%20divided%20by%20population)%20between%202011-12%20and%202022-23%20has%20increased%20by%20more%20than%2060%25%20but%20the%20incomes%20of%20the%20poor%20has%20barely%20risen%20%E2%80%94%2034%25%20of%20households%20earn%20less%20than%20the%20national%20minimum%20floor%20wage%20%E2%80%94%20which%20means%20that%20%E2%80%9CGDP%20growth%20has%20only%20benefited%20the%20rich%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Flakh-aspirants-jobs-exams-constable-recruitment%5C%22%3E48%20Lakh%20Aspirants%20For%2067%2C000%20Jobs%3A%20How%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Conducted%20the%20Constable%20Recruitment%20Exam%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20top%2010%25%20held%2063%25%20of%20the%20national%20wealth%20in%202012%20and%20it%20increased%20to%2064.5%25%20in%202022.%20In%202012%2C%20the%20bottom%2050%25%20held%206.1%25%20of%20the%20national%20wealth%20and%20it%20has%20dropped%20down%20to%205.6%25%20in%202022%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civic%20action%20forum%20underlined%20that%20the%20government%20should%20ensure%20right%20to%20food%20for%20all%3B%20right%20to%20employment%20with%20living%20wages%20and%20timely%20payment%20of%20wages%20for%20all%3B%20right%20to%20free%20and%20quality%20healthcare%3B%20right%20to%20free%20and%20quality%20education%3B%20right%20to%20pensions.%20Further%2C%20in%20order%20to%20fulfil%20these%20social-economic%20initiatives%2C%20Bahutva%20Karnataka%20proposed%20that%2010%25%20of%20the%20GDP%20should%20be%20allocated%20for%20social%20security.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20current%20sources%20of%20funding%2C%20these%20measures%20can%20be%20funded%20through%20a%20wealth%20tax%20of%202%25%20and%2033.3%25%20inheritance%20tax%20on%20the%20top%201%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20the%20forum%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710327642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F29174355%2F20240123_092445.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Findians-forced-to-resort-to-low-paying-self-employment-as-well-paying-jobs-have-declined-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20civic%20action%20forum%20in%20a%20recently%20released%20report%20busted%20several%20claims%20made%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20over%20the%20years%20on%20the%20status%20of%20employment%2C%20national%20minimum%20floor%20wage%20and%20GDP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Findians-forced-to-resort-to-low-paying-self-employment-as-well-paying-jobs-have-declined-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nigerian%20Islamic%20police%20arrest%20non-fasting%20Muslims%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710327307000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1569E%2Fproduction%2F_132901778_7af49ccd-0440-4ea1-8444-961ffc44f832.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68552431%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2011%20violated%20the%20Ramadan%20fast%20in%20northern%20Kano%20state%2C%20where%20Sharia%20operates%20alongside%20secular%20law.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A519%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68552431%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.u