%20over%20as%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20(CEC)%20in%20due%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20unattributed%20reports%2C%20he%20resigned%20(or%20was%20prevailed%20upon%20to%20quit)%20because%20of%20serious%20differences%20with%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAshok%20Lavasa%E2%80%99s%20resignation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Ashok%20Lavasa%20was%20appointed%20an%20EC.%20He%20gave%20several%20dissenting%20notes%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20infringement%20of%20the%20campaigning%20rules%20the%202019%20election.%20He%20resigned%20in%20August%202020%20and%20went%20on%20to%20join%20the%20Asian%20Development%20Bank%20as%20vice%20president%2C%20a%20position%20normally%20filled%20with%20government%20backing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDivya%20Trivedi%E2%80%99s%20article%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F367f8f63-4fe7-4b33-b36e-2aea066ac1be%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F367f8f63-4fe7-4b33-b36e-2aea066ac1be%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1710402127301000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw36H3fymdxF79m75GN3Wcyx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CAshok%20Lavasa%3A%20Targeting%20a%20dissenter%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EFrontline%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20October%2010%2C%202019%2C%20noted%20with%20anguish%20that%20Lavasa%2C%20who%20was%20the%20sole%20EC%20who%20did%20not%20agree%20to%20give%20a%20clean%20chit%20to%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20for%20their%20acts%20of%20commission%20and%20omission%20during%20the%20election%20campaign%2C%20%E2%80%9Cseemed%20to%20be%20paying%20the%20price%20for%20his%20dissent%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20then%20noted%20that%20investigations%20were%20initiated%20against%20five%20members%20of%20his%20family%20by%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department.%20He%20was%20also%20one%20of%20those%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F6e7bffd8-5768-4cc3-acba-19d57f03b92c%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F6e7bffd8-5768-4cc3-acba-19d57f03b92c%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1710402127301000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2LlVElOTqcp0HhVOD3GMt9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etargeted%20with%20Pegasus%20spyware%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20extraordinary%20that%20two%20ECs%20have%20resigned%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20tenure%2C%20indicating%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms%20that%20all%20is%20not%20well%20with%20a%20body%20which%20is%20mandated%20to%20conduct%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20which%20in%20turn%20have%20been%20held%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20constitution%E2%80%99s%20basic%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20commanded%20high%20respect%20and%20admiration%20from%20within%20India%20and%20abroad%20and%20during%20its%20golden%20jubilee%20celebrations%20in%202000%2C%20former%20President%20K.R.%20Narayanan%20quoted%20a%20public%20opinion%20poll%20according%20to%20which%20people%20rated%20the%20Election%20Commission%20very%20highly%20%E2%80%93%20far%20ahead%20of%20the%20police%2C%20the%20bureaucracy%2C%20political%20parties%2C%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20local%20self%20government%20and%20even%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EApprehensions%20expressed%20in%20Constituent%20Assembly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArun%20Goel%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20and%20Lavasa%E2%80%99s%20earlier%20resignation%20are%20part%20of%20the%20unmistakable%20trend%20of%20the%20decline%20and%20fall%20of%20the%20high%20benchmarks%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20impartiality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20with%20retrospect%2C%20the%20alarming%20collapse%20of%20the%20commission%E2%80%99s%20independence%20reflects%20apprehensions%20of%20two%20distinguished%20members%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%2C%20Shibban%20Lal%20Saxena%20and%20Hriday%20Nath%20Kunzru%2C%20as%20well%20as%20of%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20drafting%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2015%2C%201949%2C%20during%20the%20discussion%20on%20Article%20289%20in%20the%20draft%20constitution%2C%20which%20concerned%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20Saxena%20presciently%20but%20poignantly%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20quite%20possible%20that%20some%20party%20in%20power%20who%20wants%20to%20win%20the%20next%20election%20may%20appoint%20a%20staunch%20party%20man%20as%20chief%20commissioner.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20with%20sadness%20could%20foresee%20a%20period%20in%20the%20evolution%20of%20our%20country%20when%20there%20might%20not%20be%20another%20prime%20minister%20like%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20who%20was%20known%20for%20his%20independence%20and%20impartiality%2C%20and%20when%20someone%20getting%20elected%20to%20that%20office%20might%20abuse%20their%20power%20and%20authority%20by%20appointing%20an%20unworthy%20EC%2C%20subverting%20the%20electoral%20process%20and%20the%20very%20foundation%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20later%2C%20on%20June%2016%2C%20Kunzru%20in%20his%20speech%20warned%20that%20if%20the%20electoral%20machinery%20would%20become%20defective%2C%20inefficient%20or%20be%20run%20by%20people%20of%20doubtful%20integrity%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdemocracy%20will%20be%20poisoned%20at%20the%20source%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20cautioned%20that%20instead%20of%20learning%20how%20the%20judicious%20use%20of%20their%20vote%20can%20reform%20the%20administration%2C%20people%20should%20not%20end%20up%20learning%20how%20to%20get%20what%20they%20want%20through%20intrigue%20and%20unfair%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmbedkar%E2%80%99s%20apprehensions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbedkar%20feared%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20might%20%E2%80%9Ccome%20under%20the%20thumb%20of%20the%20executive%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20provision%20in%20the%20constitution%20preventing%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day%20from%20appointing%20unworthy%20people%20to%20the%20poll%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20its%20order%20of%20March%202023%20reiterated%20those%20apprehensions%20when%20it%20said%20that%20to%20prevent%20the%20Election%20Commission%20from%20becoming%20%E2%80%9Ca%20servile%20commission%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20committee%20consisting%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20and%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20or%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20party%20with%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20MPs%20should%20recommend%20candidates%20for%20appointment%20to%20the%20poll%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETragically%2C%20the%20Modi%20regime%E2%80%99s%20law%20replaced%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20with%20a%20Union%20minister%20to%20be%20chosen%20by%20the%20prime%20minister.%20The%20resignations%20of%20two%20ECs%20and%20the%20alteration%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order%20during%20the%20Modi%20regime%20form%20part%20of%20the%20alarming%20pattern%20of%20the%20decline%20of%20our%20democracy%E2%80%99s%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20Sahu%20served%20as%20an%20officer%20on%20special%20duty%20to%20former%20President%20K.R.%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710318647000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13134450%2Fimage-1945.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fg