a%20Mishra%2C%20who%20had%20prior%20experience%20of%20running%20a%20consumer%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNeeraj%20and%20Nikhil%20were%20only%2026%20and%2027%20respectively%20when%20they%20founded%20SolarSquare%20in%202015.%20In%20the%20same%20year%2C%20I%20founded%20Flyrobe%2C%20a%20fashion%20rental%20startup.%20It%20was%20very%20different%20from%20the%20world%20of%20solar%20energy.%20I%20sold%20my%20startup%20in%202019%2C%20and%20in%20the%20following%20year%2C%20my%20husband%20Neeraj%20convinced%20me%20to%20join%20SolarSquare.%20He%20was%20an%20engineer%20with%20banking%20experience%20but%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20with%20deep%20meaning%20and%20purpose.%20While%20he%20had%20a%20good%20grasp%20of%20the%20solar%20market%2C%20he%20wanted%20my%20expertise%20in%20building%20consumer%20businesses.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20we%20started%20experimenting%20in%20the%20residential%20solar%20segment%2C%20which%20is%20more%20B2C%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Shreya%2C%20co-founder%20of%20SolarSquare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20going%20to%20be%20a%20tough%20pivot%20because%20the%20industrial%20segment%20is%20very%20different.%20As%20a%20company%20in%20the%20commercial%20and%20industrial%20segment%2C%20SolarSquare%20was%20setting%20up%20massive%20and%20customised%20solar%20power%20installations%20worth%20a%20few%20crores%20for%20Fortune%20500%20companies.%20This%20is%20unlike%20the%20residential%20sector%20where%20they%20are%20dealing%20with%20individual%20homeowners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNeeraj%20and%20Nikhil%20took%20a%20very%20bold%20call%20to%20experiment%20in%20the%20residential%20solar%20segment%20because%20they%20understood%20the%20massive%20business%20opportunity%20it%20offered%20at%20a%20time%20when%20no%20organised%20company%20in%20the%20solar%20energy%20space%20saw%20it.%20They%20saw%20that%20the%20residential%20solar%20segment%20looked%20like%20the%20opportunity%20of%20the%20future.%20If%20they%20were%20to%20commit%20to%20this%2C%20they%20had%20to%20focus%20all%20their%20energies%20on%20it.%20That%20was%20a%20major%20inflexion%20point%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residential%20solar%20segment%20presented%20the%20opportunity%20of%20the%20future%20because%20average%20Indian%20households%20were%20struggling%20with%20rising%20electricity%20bills%20thanks%20to%20increasing%20tariffs%20and%20regular%20incidences%20of%20extreme%20weather%20conditions.%20Rising%20electricity%20costs%20in%20many%20states%20made%20it%20imperative%20for%20consumers%20to%20explore%20alternative%20solutions.%20One%20viable%20solution%20for%20individual%20homeowners%20and%20residential%20societies%20was%20to%20adopt%20rooftop%20solar%20power%20installations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Shreya%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20residential%20segment%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20built%20a%20lot%20of%20standardisation%20in%20solar%20installations%20that%20has%20allowed%20us%20to%20scale.%20Imagine%20doing%20tiny%20solar%20installations%20that%20are%20customised%20to%20each%20home!%20It%E2%80%99s%20too%20complex%20a%20process%20for%20a%20B2C%20operation.%20We%20standardised%20everything%20and%20made%20prefabricated%20ready-to-install%20solar%20kits%2C%20which%20get%20installed%20in%20just%20six%20hours.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20we%20underwent%20a%20lot%20of%20learning%20innovation%20for%20this%20segment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarely%20three%20and%20half%20years%20later%2C%20SolarSquare%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20leading%20residential%20solar%20brand%20in%20India%20with%20a%20consumer%20base%20of%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20individual%20homeowners%20and%20over%20100%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311732%2Fmumbai-sustainable-housing-society-saves-water-electricity-navin-chandra-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresidential%20societies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20Shreya%20claims%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20serendipity%20led%20us%20here.%20Today%2C%20we%20are%20operational%20in%2016%20cities%20spread%20across%20eight%20states.%20Over%20two%20rounds%20of%20funding%2C%20we%20have%20raised%20about%20Rs%20130%20crore%20and%20we%E2%80%99ll%20be%20doing%20close%20to%20Rs%20200%20crore%20in%20revenues%20in%20this%20financial%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20about%2020%25%20of%20SolarSquare%E2%80%99s%20business%20still%20lies%20in%20the%20commercial%20and%20industrial%20solar%20segment%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20pivoted%20close%20to%2080%25%20of%20their%20business%20towards%20the%20residential%20segment.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20they%20have%20also%20doubled%20in%20size%20as%20a%20business%20%E2%80%94%20a%20significant%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%2080%25%20of%20our%20business%20is%20in%20the%20residential%20segment%20where%20we%20work%20with%20individual%20homes%20(2BHK%2C%203BHK)%20and%20residential%20societies.%20RWAs%20buy%20solar%20power%20installations%20for%20their%20common%20areas%20like%20lifts%2C%20water%20pumps%2C%20street%20lights%2C%20etc.%20Many%20of%20the%20high-rise%20apartments%20you%20see%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20Bengaluru%20are%20SolarSquare%20customers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1709904299.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zero%20electricity%20with%20solar%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1709904299.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1709904299-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1709904299-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1709904299-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1709904299-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344445%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20SolarSquare%20Team%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20doubt%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202024%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20that%20the%20Union%20Government%20had%20set%20a%20target%20of%20installing%20rooftop%20solar%20in%20one%20crore%20households%20over%20the%20next%20few%20months.%20When%20SolarSquare%20decided%20to%20pivot%20to%20the%20residential%20solar%20segment%20in%20late%202020%2C%20this%20major%20market%20opportunity%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20apparent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20families%20weren%E2%80%99t%20aware%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20solar.%20People%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20basics.%20Many%20people%20confuse%20rooftop%20solar%20installations%20with%20water%20heaters.%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20you%20could%20power%20your%20home%20with%20solar.%20There%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20myths%20and%20misconceptions%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20addressed%20and%20awareness%20levels%20were%20very%20nascent%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolarSquare%E2%80%99s%20first%20mandate%20was%20to%20create%20a%20brand%20on%20the%20back%20of%20%E2%80%9Ceducational%20marketing%20and%20trust.%E2%80%9D%20To%20that%20end%2C%20they%20published%20videos%2C%20content%2C%20and%20blogs%2C%20and%20worked%20with%20influencers%20to%20create%20awareness.%20They%20have%20also%20published%20a%20free%20homeowner%E2%80%99s%20guide%20to%20going%20solar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20installing%20anything%2C%20we%20will%20help%20a%20homeowner%20understand%20why%20solar%20is%20good%20for%20them%20and%20what%20kind%20of%20solar%20installation%20is%20good%20for%20their%20home.%20We%20decided%20that%20we%20would%20first%20educate%20people%20before%20selling%20them%20anything.%20See%2C%20there%20was%20rampant%20mis-selling%20in%20this%20industry.%20Residential%20solar%20is%20a%20fragmented%20and%20unorganised%20market%20involving%20a%20lot%20of%20local%20operators%20who%20do%20this%20as%20a%20side%20business.%20People%20were%20sold%20second%20hand%20or%20rejected%20panels%20because%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20authenticate%20warranty%20or%20quality%20of%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20many%20were%20sold%20solar%20power%20installations%20without%20after-sales%20service.%20If%20you%20are%20buying%20solar%2C%20buying%20the%20right%20after-sales%20service%20is%20very%20important%20because%2C%20without%20it%2C%20your%20investment%20goes%20down%20the%20drain.%20We%20had%20to%20educate%20people%20about%20these%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20biggest%20challenge%20for%20SolarSquare%20was%20convincing%20potential%20investors%20that%20their%20decision%20to%20foray%20into%20the%20residential%20segment%20made%20business%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20went%20out%20to%20raise%20funds%2C%20potential%20investors%20thought%20that%20residential%20solar%20is%20a%20small%20market.%20Most%20of%20them%20were%20more%20engaged%20in%20fintech%20and%20e-commerce.%20They%20felt%20that%20residential%20solar%20was%20a%20very%20brick-and-mortar%20business%20where%20you%20have%20to%20go%20from%20one%20home%20to%20another%2C%20educate%20people%2C%20close%20an%20order%2C%20install%20panels%20at%20their%20homes%2C%20and%20maintain%20them%20for%20years.%20Nobody%20understood%20this%20market%20and%20its%20potential%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Neeraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EForbes%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20June%202022%2C%20Shreya%20claimed%20that%20residential%20solar%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98%2450%20billion%20opportunity%E2%80%99%20based%20on%20her%20estimates.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20bold%20claim%20back%20then%20given%20how%20international%20market%20research%20and%20advisory%20companies%20like%20%3Cem%3ECustom%20Market%20Insights%3C%2Fem%3E%20estimated%20that%20the%20entire%20Indian%20solar%20energy%20market%20was%20worth%20%2438%20billion%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLooking%20back%2C%20I%20probably%20wildly%20underestimated%20the%20market.%20With%20one%20crore%20homes%20potentially%20going%20solar%20in%20the%20next%20three%20years%2C%20this%20market%20will%20probably%20see%20%2425%20billion.%20In%20a%20decade%2C%20this%20could%20very%20well%20be%20a%20%2475%20billion%20to%20%24100%20billion%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20unique%20time%20in%20history%20where%20you%20can%20create%20a%20consumer%20brand%20in%20energy.%20Otherwise%2C%20energy%20has%20always%20been%20the%20game%20of%20large%20corporations%20and%20Government-owned%20power%20plants.%20Energy%20is%20now%20personal%20and%20private%2C%20and%20we%20can%20create%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289075%2Fisb-grad-helps-large-fmcg-brands-recycle-plastic-packaging-reduce-waste%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsumer%20brand%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20it.%20Investors%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20to%20build%20their%20understanding%20of%20the%20possibilities%20in%20this%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1-1709904418.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22You%20will%20get%20zero%20electricity%20bill%20by%20going%20solar%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1-1709904418.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1-1709904418-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1-1709904418-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1-1709904418-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FSolarSquare-Team-1-1709904418-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344449%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESolarSquare%3A%20Helping%20homeowners%20go%20solar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20go%20solar%20with%20SolarSquare%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20can%20a%20homeowner%20in%20India%20install%20solar%20power%20in%20their%20homes%20with%20SolarSquare%3F%20A%20journey%20with%20them%20begins%20with%20registering%20an%20inquiry%20either%20on%20their%20website%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303367%2Fbengaluru-women-teach-how-to-compost-grow-vegetables-at-home-using-whatsapp-group-urban-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhatsApp%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Once%20customers%20register%20a%20query%2C%20SolarSquare%20sets%20up%20a%20%E2%80%98free%20solar%20consultation%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20solar%20consultant%2C%20a%20trained%20expert%2C%20will%20visit%20your%20home%2C%20survey%20your%20roof%2C%20understand%20your%20electricity%20requirements%2C%20study%20your%20electricity%20bills%2C%20and%20guide%20you%20to%20the%20right%20solar%20solution%20for%20your%20home.%20They%20will%20also%20explain%20how%20solar%20power%20works%2C%20what%20are%20the%20different%20technology%20choices%20available%2C%20etc.%20We%20consult%20the%20customer